Steve Madely is an Ottawa, Ontario radio host on CFRA. He got his start in 1964 at CHWO in Oakville, Ontario before eventually joining CFRA in 1981. He is the host of the station's weekday morning show Madely in the Morning, weekdays from 6am to 9am. The show features Madely's top five stories of the day which are reiterated over the show, a 10 minute long listener call-in session at 6:40, health headlines at 6:55, and weird and wacky stories at 7:55. 
